data.content:
Boyfriend
Boyfriend was the narrator’s intersex partner who disappeared after the narrator discovered the narrator’s intersex status.<SEP>Boyfriend is a partner of the Narrator who disappears after the pregnancy announcement.

2000
2000 is the year of the narrator’s birth and the origin point of the time loop.

Grandfather
Grandfather was the narrator’s grandfather who was murdered by a masked killer at age nine and left a letter with instructions for the narrator.

Masked Shark
Masked Shark is a masked killer who murdered Grandfather at the narrator’s age of nine and was later killed by the narrator in 2009.

Time Travel
Time Travel is the mechanism that allows the narrator to move across specific years to maintain timeline integrity.

Child
Child is the narrator’s child, born at age 24, later stolen, and subsequently used to close the time loop.<SEP>Child is the offspring of the Narrator, born in 2024, who is later stolen.

Letter
Letter is a written message given by Grandfather to the narrator, to be opened on the 27th birthday, containing instructions for survival and time travel.

Me
The narrator, known as “Me”, experiences multiple time‑travel events, identity transformations, and orchestrates actions to preserve the timeline.

2009
2009 is the year when Grandfather was murdered and the narrator returns to eliminate the masked killer.

2023
2023 is the year when the narrator first time‑travels to romance a female version of self and secure a pregnancy.

Car Accident
An automobile collision at age 27 that caused the narrator to become fully male.<SEP>Car Accident is an incident involving the Narrator in 2027, resulting in surgery.

Death of Me
The narrator’s death before handing over the letter to the younger self.

2024
2024 is the year when the narrator notices resemblance to Grandfather and prepares for the final closure.

Time Loop
The closed cyclical sequence of events that the narrator must preserve to avoid disappearance.

27th Birthday
27th Birthday is the pivotal moment for opening the letter and initiating the time‑travel cycle.<SEP>27th Birthday is the event on which the Narrator is 27 years old, occurring in 2027.

Female Self
Female Self is the narrator’s self at age 27 in the 2023 iteration, whose pregnancy and birth are essential to the timeline.

Narrator
The Narrator is an individual born in 2000, who experiences significant life events and ultimately discovers their parents.

Grandpa's Letter
Grandpa's Letter is a written message given to the Narrator before Grandpa's death, to be opened on the Narrator's 27th birthday.

Masked Person
Masked Person is an unnamed individual who murders Grandpa in 2009.

Grandpa
Grandpa is the Narrator's only living relative at birth, who foretells future family encounters.

Parents
Parents are the biological parents of the Narrator, discovered after opening Grandpa's Letter.

Surgery
Surgery is a medical procedure performed on the Narrator following the Car Accident.

Boyfriend Disappearance
The disappearance of the Boyfriend after the pregnancy announcement.

2009 Adoption
The adoption of the Narrator following Grandpa's death.

2024 Child Theft
The theft of the Narrator's child in 2024.

2023 Pregnancy
The Narrator's pregnancy announcement in 2023.

Grandpa's Death
The death of Grandpa in 2009.

2000 Birth
The Narrator's birth event occurring in 2000.
